        "intro-text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We stayed small so your dog sees the same face every visit. The four of us split the calendar — Mara takes doodles and anxious dogs, Dani runs double coats, Rae handles puppies and small breeds, Jules runs the bath and walk-in nails.</p><p>Your dog gets matched to a groomer at intake, then stays with that person for as long as they're a regular. Continuity matters more than schedule magic.</p>",
            "size": "base",
            "uppercase": false,
            "muted": false
          }
        },
        "intro-button": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "link": {
              "text": "Book with us",
              "href": "contact.html",
              "target": "_self"
