            "specialty": "Doodles · hand-stripping · anxious dogs",
            "bio": "Twelve years in two other shops before opening Pawlish in 2017. Specializes in doodle teddy cuts, terrier hand-stripping, and the slow work nervous dogs need. NDGAA certified. The person to ask if your dog has been turned away elsewhere.",
